.TH g-workspace-switch 1  "g-workspace-switch " 
.SH NAME
g\-workspace\-switch \- Open a subshell in a workspace directory
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBg\-workspace\-switch\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fINAME\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Open a subshell in a workspace directory
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
[\fINAME\fR]
Workspace name (fuzzy matched). Omit to open an interactive picker
